story_txt:
The project focuses on development of innovative on-line role game with elements of shooter and other styles, including educational elements. The design philosophy provides different players with the chance to play together in our world. The project will support possible shift of the user’s interest during the game, provide both convenient mechanisms of such shift and possibility of different types of users’ coexistence in a single space. Game environment will hardly compel or limit them.The company’s project is a mass on-line game with educational elements. The communicative background of the project is virtual reality that represents different territories.All actions of the game take place in the real time three dimension spaces, except for some actions held in specific interfaces, such as economic aspects. The logic of the game environment is successively built by means of property factors and principles, revealed by the project originators, such as capital, money, law, power, private property, etc., that characterize modern world order. The environment, constructed in such a way, will encourage different activities in the form they exist in reality, stimulating working with complex institutional objects.The game is basically    RPG one, with elements of 3D shooter and the main idea of technocracy (science fiction). MMORPG/MMOFPS.
3D – shooter (the basis is shooter with partial solo game);
Tactical shooter (the basis is team actions);
Stealth action (avoiding of possible hostile contact);
Economy (real economy emulation. Elements of MMORTS);
Adventure (quests, based on the game plot;
Specific quests;
Role play – RPG (development of the personage’s skills, elements of MMORPG).
The company plans to use the hybrid business-model of service monetization with an accent upon the free-to-play component.Competitiveness of the developed game is caused by the following factors:
the game represents a new trend in the game industry.  Essentially, it is birth of a new game style.
the project is developed for a large number of users:
- people, who search for new knowledge in different spheres;
- people, who search for new experiences, feelings and emotions;
- gamers.
- solves a problem of comprehensibility and improvement of quality of information perception by participants of the project (solves problems of availability of the gained knowledge to the large number of people, taking into account dispensing, categorization, relevance, definition of the necessary information to eachparticipant of the project);- solves problems of interaction of communities (small, average, big) in various directions (from private, to general), solving the problems of the game.
solves problems of availability of knowledge to the wide mass of people;
deals with problems of real IT tendencies;
is engaged in promoting and development of scientific activity.
Examples of technological advantages of the project:
tools for creation of own, unique game elements;
flexibility - the scalable and flexible interface in control, easily adaptable;
 use of experimental theory of training (training, based on experience).

Project of the global scale;
localization;
encouragement of any user’s participation ;
stimulation of personal progress of the user;
diversity of functions and flexibility;
reliability;
safety;
constant development of the project.
